---
import BlogLayout from '../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
---

<BlogLayout title="About" description="About Michael LaPlante — SVP of Information Security and Operations.">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <div class="about-card">
    <img
      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/laplantedev/image/upload/w_200,h_200,c_fill,g_face,r_max,f_auto/v1732243228/2023-inductees-la-plante-square_wwy6ir.jpg"
      alt="Michael LaPlante"
      class="about-photo"
    />
    <div class="about-info">
      <h2>Michael LaPlante</h2>
      <p class="about-role">SVP of Information Security and Operations</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    I'm a technology executive with over 15 years of experience spanning
    information security, engineering leadership, and software development.
    I currently serve as SVP of Information Security and Operations at Proforma,
    where I oversee security strategy, infrastructure, and engineering teams.
  </p>

  <p>
    Before moving into security leadership, I spent years as a hands-on engineer
    building web applications, leading development teams, and teaching others to code.
    That engineering background shapes how I approach security — pragmatically,
    with an emphasis on building secure systems rather than bolting security on after the fact.
  </p>

  <p>
    This blog covers what I'm thinking about: security trends, engineering practices,
    and the tools I use to build things. Sometimes I write about the process itself —
    how AI-assisted development is changing the way I work.
  </p>

  <div class="about-links">
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mlaplante/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/mlaplante" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    <a href="https://twitter.com/laplantewebdev" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>
    <a href="/">Portfolio</a>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>

<style>
  .about-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-info h2 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .about-role {
    font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  p {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .about-links a {
    font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #2980b9;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .about-links a:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .about-info h2 { color: #f1f5f9; }
    .about-role { color: #94a3b8; }
    p { color: #cbd5e1; }
    .about-links { border-top-color: #1e293b; }
    .about-links a { color: #60a5fa; }
    .about-photo { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
